categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: In 22 BBY, a Rodian Jedi was present at the briefing led by Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi prior to the First Battle of Kamino. The Rodian flew a Delta-7 light interceptor with a team of other Jedi as part of the starfighter defense of Kamino.
